 Cocteau Twins 宣布重新发行《月亮与旋律》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/cocteau-twins-announce-the-moon-and-the-melodies-reissue-3773429?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=cocteau-twins-announce-the-moon-和旋律重新发行Surej SinghWed, 10 Jul 2024 03:58:03 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3773429 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="苏格兰另类摇滚乐队 Cocteau Twins，Clapham Junction，英国伦敦，1993 年" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>自 1986 年发行以来，哈罗德·巴德 (Harold Budd) 的合作将首次推出黑胶唱片</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cocteau-twins-announce-the-moon-and-the-melodies-reissue-3773429">Cocteau Twins 宣布重新发行《月亮与旋律》</a>后，首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发表。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="苏格兰另类摇滚乐队 Cocteau Twins，Clapham Junction，英国伦敦，1993 年" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696