 Wunderhorse 分享反思新单曲“Silver” https://www.nme.com/news/music/wunderhorse-share-reflect-new-single-silver-3773384?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=wunderhorse-share-reflect-new-single-silverAnagricel Duran Tue, 09 Jul 2024 21:03:09 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3773384 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="神马。图片来源：波洛乔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌是乐队第二张专辑《Midas》中发行的第三首歌曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wunderhorse-share-reflective-new-single-silver-3773384">Wunderhorse 分享的反思性新单曲“Silver”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="神马。图片来源：波洛乔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wunderhorse.-Credit-Polocho-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a>分享了他们即将发行的第二张专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wunderhorse-announce-second-album-midas-and-share-heavy-new-single-july-3757045">Midas</a> ”中的反思性新单曲“Silver”。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/wunderhorse-band-interview-new-album-midas-3766063">Wunderhorse 如何团结在一起：“你们必须互相照顾。这是一个竞争激烈的行业”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 《Silver》以清脆的吉他和弦开场，主唱雅各布·斯莱特 (Jacob Slater) 唱道： <em>“是的，我从摇篮起就弯曲/我从一开始就是个私生子/我保留了一些漂亮的人/在我的内心空洞中，”</em>反思他自己。</p><p>据一份新闻稿称，这首歌几乎没有出现在“Midas”中，因为它感觉与唱片不相称。该乐队由 Slater、吉他手 Harry Fowler、鼓手 Jamie Staples 和贝斯手 Pete Woodin 组成，最终在明尼苏达州的 Pachyderm Studios 工作时剥离了这首歌，并找到了最终的形式。</p><p>在新闻稿中谈到《Silver》时，斯莱特说：“这首歌讲述的是你自己丑陋的一面，你试图保守秘密，但你知道它的存在，因为它有时会让你起鸡皮疙瘩。它让你获得了位置，但在这个过程中却把你搞砸了。每个人都有自己不愿承认或隐藏起来从不去看的化妆元素。这就是“银”的含义。有点儿。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="神马 - 银" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WWYjGH6fW5c?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>由 Polocho 执导，这首歌的音乐视频中斯莱特坐在玩具屋里，旁边是一只笼中的鸟，而有人透过窗户往里看。还可以看到他们之前的音乐视频中出现的其他主题，例如摇马和玩具猴子。</p><p> 《Silver》是《Midas》继《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wunderhorse-announce-second-album-midas-and-share-heavy-new-single-july-3757045">July</a> 》及其 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-wunderhorses-bluesy-new-single-midas-2-3616648">主打歌</a>之后发行的第三首单曲。该密纹唱片定于 8 月 30 日发行，可<a href="https://wunderhorseband.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预存/预订</a>。</p><p>此前谈到这张专辑的创作时，斯莱特说道：“当我们第一次走进录音室制作这张唱片时，我们唯一确定的是我们想要它听起来如何；非常不完美，非常生动，非常原始；没有多余的装饰。我们希望它听起来就像你的脸压在放大器上，就像你被锁在低音鼓里一样。”</p><p> 《Midas》继 2022 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/wunderhorse-cub-review-jacob-slater-radar-3319474">Cub</a> 》之后。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/wunderhorse-cub-review-jacob-slater-radar-3319474">对该专辑的四星评论中，</a> <em>NME</em>分享道：“[这张专辑]是对我们之前认识的 Jacob Slater 的告别，也是对一位终于成为自己的歌曲作者的非常令人兴奋的欢迎。你可以想象他在未来几十年里都会创造这样的唱片。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C7Bgn7VA8As/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 